{"tid":27761,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個路試肥佬經驗","createTime":"2016-12-07T13:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T07:59:42.000Z","uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46bd26f6f5f60ff989d124c3e0626bf58a31a03e","tid":27761,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:47:30.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次考油塘落山果條線係高駿苑過紅VAN冇為意對面線有九巴上緊山，而我又冇即時停車讓路，咁就衰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n集思廣益，等學緊未考或者準備再考既巴打汲取教訓，避免再比運豬署又賺多次510"},{"pid":"abeeee6969e503fdb4561af52cbb070ed7d410f7","tid":27761,"uid":43717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:54:53.000Z","msg":"想衝燈尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />結果佢踩停我之後成四五秒都未轉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二次再考背曬沿途交通燈，一望對面行人公仔就知自己要去埋定拖慢"},{"pid":"c861640273620c306e321c400fcddb94a2ed764b","tid":27761,"uid":4466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:56:57.000Z","msg":"無上三波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983fb0ac16eca71f6b9fd0ef18a9610e3692b823","tid":27761,"uid":50674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:58:24.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6d35448f21438ddaf0c17da77899dd413318a6","tid":27761,"uid":33851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:28:16.000Z","msg":"天光道考場，一開波要轉左去做泊位<br />\n我戇鳩鳩比架車向前，然後被一腳踩停<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99342626afe89b82569b9c5eb16f0ae64fda2c45","tid":27761,"uid":36286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次考油塘落山果條線係高駿苑過紅VAN冇為意對面線有九巴上緊山，而我又冇即時停車讓路，咁就