=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a06ce8ab29bdbeff547263cb35406cc2238fb5","tid":27761,"uid":30972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:30:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係肥佬經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我考嗰陣考官話我溜後 我堅持話冇 <br />\n但佢話有 跟住我俾佢睇我未放hand brake<br />\n<br />\n佢哦左聲就全程唔理我 連帶路都冇 最後pass左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2375d9921f689403fffba96d298f29eb668b947c","tid":27761,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:33:47.000Z","msg":"遊䲰魂定太緊張，路口唔記得要轉左。"},{"pid":"53a082836fd06b61a8f2528bf1a82401bdaf5dea","tid":27761,"uid":58825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:40:52.000Z","msg":"考葵盛圍3次先合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW 我第一次明明擰晒頭 望晒鏡 沿路又冇突發情況 點知個考官話我因爲冇望左邊盲點肥左我 <br />\n其實考貨van 好似左邊盲點可以唔使望"},{"pid":"acddbe1c691ce9b062228f0dd0d4df17f4b9a49e","tid":27761,"uid":22557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:43:19.000Z","msg":"考永孝街<br />\n呔盤使用不正確<br />\n唔知自己衰咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8969e043aa727ef3782e0b2481a3d86cc576d81","tid":27761,"uid":34500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:43:47.000Z","msg":"我都想請講<br />\n<br />\n可惜我1take pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21f633373ae9148529be024ab0fa9c893ba32fd","tid":27761,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:42:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次衰比紅van佬亂泊街<br />\n<br />\n要係兩架紅van中間過<br />\n<br />\n最後都係死左</blockquote><br />\n咁考官有冇比指示你？定係自己決定黎？<br />\n<br />\n呢D情況我打死都唔行，夾硬過即係騎晒兩條行車線，衰硬"},{"pid":"b1f1d6e7a00f47fdf298cca05158077bcbb42856","tid":27761,"uid":26778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:50:35.000Z","msg":"點樣係路邊試肥佬 加d雞汁<img s